Package: dynamicGP
Title: Dynamic Mode Decomposition for Plant Phenomics
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements Dynamic Mode Decomposition (DMD) for fitting linear
    time-invariant state-space models to multivariate time-series data.
    run_dmd() decomposes a state sequence into DMD modes, eigenvalues, growth
    rates and oscillation frequencies. Utility functions cover multi-step state
    reconstruction, trajectory statistics, array reshaping, and spectral
    stability enforcement. Also provides greml_heritability() for computing
    SNP-based heritability via GREML using either a pure-R backend (gaston) or
    an optional GCTA binary backend.
